column4:
手錶、懷錶及其他錶，包括碼錶在內，其外殼為貴金屬
或被覆貴金屬之金屬製者
Wrist-watches, pocket-watches and other watches,
including stop-watches, with case of precious
metal or of metal clad with precious metal

not incorporating a stop-watch facility:
